x10.matrix.block

Class MatrixBlock

  • x10.lang.Object
    • x10.matrix.block.MatrixBlock
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DenseBlock, SparseBlock

    abstract public class MatrixBlock
extends x10.lang.Object
    Matrix block provides an abstraction of matrix block classes, which serves as the base classes for dense block matrix and sparse block matrix class. It can be used to build dense-sparse mixed matrix blocks too.
